\begin{align*}(1-p_n)^n&=\sum_{j\geq 0}{n\choose j}(-p_n)^j\\\\&= \sum_{j\geq 0}\left[n(n-1)\cdots(n-j+1)\over n^j\right](-np_n)^j/j!\\\\ &\to \sum_{j\geq 0}(-\lambda)^j/j!\\\\&=\exp(-\lambda).\end{align*} 
